pageContext.claim: “But Adam Schiff doesn't talk about Joe Biden and his son walking away with millions of dollars from Ukraine”
pageContext.analysis: Trump has no evidence to claim former vice president Joe Biden walked away with millions from Ukraine. Biden, unlike Trump, had disclosed decades of tax returns. Hunter Biden, one of his sons, did business deals that might not have come his way if he had not been a vice president's son, but the same could be said of Trump's adult children.
